#roadTripUnited2022 Episode 2 : Agra To Lucknow
We have recently concluded our 10th all India roadtrip and 3rd #roadtripUnited with it.
It was 45 days long roadtrip, where we covered over 10000kms, meeting over 15000 bikers onground from over 500+ biking clubs during our meetups in 24 cities all over India. There were total 33 Story tellers in different parts of the ride. The motive of the ride is to promote safe riding and also a big cause that was attached to the ride this time, #SayNoToDrugs and #YesToMotorcycling. For which we partnered with STAIRS NGO and raised funds which will be used in the betterment and efforts to channel the energies of the youth through sports, recognizing Motorcycling as a sport.

Happy Father’s Day to all! Celebrating both man and machine!

Today, we honor the bond of love, respect, and legacy that defines fatherhood, not just in families, but also in passions that shape lives.

On this special day, let’s celebrate the father of all bikes, the legendary Bajaj Pulsar! which didn’t just revolutionize Indian motorcycling, but also became the inspiration behind something bigger.

Back in 2002, what began as BajajPulsar.com by @themotographer with one single web page grew into a movement and today, it stands as xBhp, India’s largest lifestyle motorcycling community. A platform built by riders, for riders, fueled by the same spirit of freedom, speed, and brotherhood that @mypulsarofficial ignited.

Here’s to the fathers who ride, the bikes we love, and the journeys that define us.

#HappyFathersDay #xBhp #motoGrapher #BajajPulsar

The Fastest Indian, @ultraviolette_automotive #F99 Hits the Silver Screen! What a thrilling and exclusive screening at PVR ICON, DLF Promenade, Delhi! As the proud community partner, we had the honor of inviting 80+ passionate bikers to witness the untold story behind the @ultraviolette_automotive #F99, from the struggles and setbacks to the record-breaking moment that crowned it The Fastest Indian.

It wasn’t just a film, it was an emotion, celebration of innovation, resilience, and speed.
